init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film is your life, and you are the star.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a baby, as a child, as a teenager, as a young adult, and so on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am very famous and very rich.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I travel to many places and meet many people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I also met a man who I fell in love with.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was a big fan of mine and was very excited to see me.
